# Copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is git-ignored ‚Äî never commit real keys.

# --- Claude (Anthropic) ---
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Apify ---
APIFY_TOKEN=apify_api_...

# --- Local dev only ---
# Path to job-apply's SQLite DB so the job engine has matches to surface.
